Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.34,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,You damned idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:47.85,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Now is not the time to mourn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.89,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,You... you still have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.93,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Now, there's no time to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.69,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,You must must go and defeat Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:10.66,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Destroy... the stone mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:11.33,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Mr. Zeppeli!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:25.68,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,I'm... satisfied with the way... my destiny played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:31.39,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,When I was a young man... I was married...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:36.86,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,However... I abandoned my family for the quest to destroy the stone mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:41.62,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,But now, I can rest in peace being satisfied with the life I led...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.41,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,I can accept what has become of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:55.15,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,In the end... at least I was able to pass on all that I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:13:02.24,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Jojo.... you are my living hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.28,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Mr. Zeppeli...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:11.35,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,I think of you as my best friend and son...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:18.29,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,...and... I will continue... to live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.65,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,...within you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.30,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Jo...
