Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:14:00.06,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And so, once again, Jojo finds himself inheriting another man's way of life... and his very spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.16,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Goodbye... Mr. Zeppeli.
