Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.27,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:55.62,Main,Sucks to be this bitch,0,0,0,,Just spare my child... I beg of you!
